## Agent / skill tooling (machine-local, not part of the resume source)
#############
.agents/
skills-lock.json
## Ignore every .claude/skill folder EXCEPT the repo-authoritative ones
## (ats-resume and ats-cover-letter), which we do want tracked.
.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/ats-resume/
!.claude/skills/ats-cover-letter/

